---
title: Creamy Tarragon Baked Chicken with Potato Wedges & Roasted Carrots
description: Tarragon might not get used in Kiwi kitchens as much as basil or parsley, but we think it’s the secret to one of the best sauces you’ll ever taste! It’s the perfect finishing touch to tasty roasted chicken and veggies.
